attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Carolyn Riley RL. Est. Srvcs, Inc.
Century 21 Carolyn Riley RL. Est. Srvcs, Inc.

data.description: Location, location, location!!! This amazing home just had new floors put in, new carpet installed on the second floor, the full bathroom has been redone, new back deck installed and the interior has been freshly painted- all within the last month!!! Situated on a quintessential Kent street, this home is a must see! Built in 1901, this 3-bedroom home has character and charm, and complete first floor living. It is quite rare to find a century home with such great closet space and high ceilings. With a primary bedroom, full bathroom and laundry room all on the first floor, it is ideal for anyone looking for convenience in living while not giving up any square footage. The primary bedroom has its own half bathroom, with direct access to the wooded backyard view. The enclosed front porch is the perfect spot for your morning coffee or your evening relaxation. The large dining room and separate living room are perfect for all of your entertaining needs, while the kitchen has everything you need for your homemade meals. The two bedrooms upstairs have natural light pouring in, along with wood floors. The huge backyard is fenced in and provides you with privacy, gardening and tons of room for fires and backyard games. Located close to downtown Kent, the University and all of the shopping and dining. Do not wait to get your showing scheduled! Call TODAY before this one is gone!
